title: Halle Pure Orchid by Halle Berry Eau De Parfum Spray for Women, 1 Ounce
description: When applying any fragrance please consider that there are several factors which can affect the natural smell of your skin and, in turn, the way a scent smells on you.  For instance, your mood, stress level, age, body chemistry, diet, and current medications may all alter the scents you wear.  Similarly, factor such as dry or oily skin can even affect the amount of time a fragrance will last after being applied

title: Reb'L Fleur by Rihanna, 3.4 Ounce, Eau De Parfum Spray
description: Reb'l Fleur is the first fragrance from rihanna. Plump fruits, red berries, purple plums and juicy, ripe peaches, make a delicious first impression, while sumptuous florals and warm base notes create an impression that is defiantly sexy.

title: Beyonce Pulse Eau De Parfum Spray for Women, 1.7 Ounce
description: Pulse by Beyonce Eau de Parfum 1.7 fl oz. Beyonce Pulse possesses an energy unlike any other. It moves through you, around you. Never fading as it surges, pulsates and electrifies. The woman who wears Beyonce Pulse is impossible to ignore, exuding sensuality and strength.

title: Selena Gomez Eau De Parfum Spray, 3.4 Ounce
description: Selena Gomez by Selena Gomez Eau De Parfum 3.4 FL OZ. Selena Gomez's self-titled new fragrance is the scented embodiment of the star herself: fresh and sweet with warmth from within. Including top notes of raspberry, peach, and pineapple, the fragrance begins as a fruity bouquet that slowly blends into heart notes of purple freesia, musk, and dewberry, before transforming into a delectable treat with rich base notes of chocolate, vanilla, and amber. Experience the Selena Gomez fragrance with this 3.4 oz Eau de Parfum Spray.
